<A>__{we roll credits over peal tight on a pattern of brown and black textures. the image begins to shake. slow motion. graceful. we hear a low rhythmic thump, thump, thump... the surface slowly peels off like flecks of dried old paint as we pull back a little wider and realize that we're looking at an old door. thump, thump, thump... the door continues to rattle. something or someone is behind it, desperately fighting to get out. thump, thump, thump... wider still to include the rusted, worn doorknob twisting back and forth and shaking. whatever is in there it's locked inside. super: hellraiser:deader}
